              "content": "<p> ADD AND EDIT: Notes from Shaykh Muḥammad in the Gambia 13 June 2022:</p><p>I mentioned the AGE OF WICKEDNNESS as spoken of in the Dead Sea Scrolls. I mentioned the Apocalyptic year seventy years before the Prophet’s birth. He affirmed the validity of my holding the opinions I do about the Age of Wickedness prior to the Age of Supreme Felicity. </p>",
